                            <comment id="141991" author="di.wang" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2016 16:50:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, it is an interop issue. So during rolling upgrade, when new OSTs communicate with old MDTs, which do not have FLD entries, so the new OSTs should stop keep trying in this case. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
